body:
I am getting the following errors with the OpenStudio component after installing version 1.9 and I have no idea why.



Does anyone have any ideas?

replies.body: This is an old issue with OpenStudio libraries and it's very unfortunate to see it back ([https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/issues/214](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/issues/214)). Which version of OpenStudio are you using? Did you make sure to unblock the OpenStudio.dll file?
